1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:02,475
Energetic music starts.

2
00:00:02,425 --> 00:00:05,975
Creator points excitedly at the camera.

3
00:00:05,975 --> 00:00:08,087
Okay, listen up!

4
00:00:08,087 --> 00:00:18,862
You see all the trading hype, the Lambos, the 'get rich quick' stories... but here's the brutal truth: Most new traders fail, and they fail FAST.

5
00:00:18,862 --> 00:00:20,075
Why?

6
00:00:20,075 --> 00:00:27,187
Because they're missing the single most fundamental, yet unsexy, pillar of profitable trading.

7
00:00:27,187 --> 00:00:30,362
And it's not some magic indicator.

8
00:00:30,362 --> 00:00:35,162
It's called **Risk Management**.

9
00:00:35,162 --> 00:00:40,787
On-screen text: ⚠️ RISK MANAGEMENT ⚠️)  Seriously!

10
00:00:40,787 --> 00:00:50,362
Before you even *think* about profits, you MUST define your maximum loss on *every single trade*.

11
00:00:50,362 --> 00:00:57,975
I never, ever risk more than 1-2% of my total trading capital on any given trade.

12
00:00:57,975 --> 00:00:59,187
EVER.

13
00:00:59,187 --> 00:01:03,225
This simple rule is your financial bodyguard.

14
00:01:03,225 --> 00:01:11,200
It means you can be wrong multiple times – which you *will* be – and still stay in the game.

15
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:16,050
You're protecting your capital, which is your ultimate resource.

16
00:01:16,050 --> 00:01:19,750
Forget chasing quick gains and FOMO.

17
00:01:19,750 --> 00:01:24,275
Focus on *not blowing up your account*.

18
00:01:24,275 --> 00:01:30,112
That's the boring, disciplined truth to building wealth consistently over time.

19
